This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias inherent in opinion-based platforms. The complexity of the issue means that not all perspectives can be fully represented in a single report. Additionally, the legal and social context of abortion rights varies significantly across different regions, which may not be fully captured in the sources used.

